5671,"uid":12432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:50:02.000Z","msg":"&quot;When a denial of a goalscoring opportunity offence is committed by a defender in the penalty area, the penalty kick effectively restores the goalscoring opportunity so the punishment for the player should be less strong (e.g. a yellow card) than when the offence is committed outside the penalty area. <span style=\"color: red;\">However, when the offence is handball or clearly not a genuine attempt to play or challenge for the ball, the player will be sent off.</span>&quot;"},{"pid":"bd858aead8750ab69d5b27e48439f9c308605ae5","tid":725671,"uid":50055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:50:26.000Z","msg":"破壞入球或明顯入球機會<br />\n當一名球員故意觸犯手球去破壞對方一個入球或明顯入球機會，無論犯規發生在<br />\n那個位置，該名犯規球員應被(紅牌)驅逐離場。<br />\n當一名球員於己方點球區域內侵犯對方球員而破壞對方一明顯入球機會時，裁判<br />\n員應判罰一點球予對方，<span style=\"color: gold;\">如該犯規是因意圖玩球時產生，犯規球員應被(黄牌)警<br />\n告</span>；但在其他情況下(例如：把持對方球員以阻礙其移動、拉對方、推對方、在沒有<br />\n玩球機會情況下等等，犯規球員必須被(紅牌)驅逐離場。"},{"pid":"1f47b4b686616f2dcaa31b0f1f98ec43f50037bf","tid":725671,"uid":82698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:55:33.000Z","msg":"改左例啦哥哥<br />\n球証覺得你全心去波就係黃牌唔洗紅<br />\n用手擋 /手球 阻止射門就必紅"},{"pid":"4a92055fe14646823ec5d55e70cb9dcbf9362de6","tid":725671,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34efcd28865d966633984fe2cf89fdd34cbcd2b1","tid":725671,"uid":67252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e9c778f9feaa5345d99a8a84610ef3b1c5504b5","tid":725671,"uid":73748,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:32:20.000Z","msg":"新例唔使食全餐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T20:33:22.000Z","msg":"龍門單刀撲跌就話姐 空門幾碼從後喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T21:22:09.000Z","msg":"咪係，龍門撲跌前鋒黃牌都合理，岩岩咁撚樣都係得黃牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\